divs: Sighting DetailsMe and my parents were watching tv then i looked out of the window and i saw these 6 to 10 orange orbs flying right behind each other heading north there was no noise at all they were flying right behind each other, not long after they disappeared i heard weird noises like trumpets and buzzing noises. i lost sight of the object when it went past the treeline.
